whitebox.cartographic

Class CartographicElementGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • whitebox.cartographic.CartographicElementGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<CartographicElement>, CartographicElement

    public class CartographicElementGroup
extends java.lang.Object
implements CartographicElement, java.lang.Comparable<CartographicElement>
    This is a container for other cartographic elements that allows for grouping, such that the elements can be treated as a single object for drawing.
